                <h3>Speech - Language Therapy</h3>
                <p>
                Speech Correction Teachers provide daily speech and language therapy to all of the children at SEMFI [PID & ISP]. They collaborate with PID & ISP teachers to develop individualized speech and language goals for each child. Speech Correction Teachers incorporate Speech therapy, aural habilitation, and academic tutoring are available to current or former PID students, and also to those enrolled in other schools. Services are provided through our Speech and Hearing Department – The SpeechLab, a One-on-one Speech Clinic.
                </p>
            </div>
            <!-- Card 2 -->
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <span class="dot"></span>
